375 ##·Introduction377 ##·Introduction
  
376 Py**T**orch·**Im**age·**M**odels·(`timm`)·is·a·collection·of·image·models,·layers,·utilities,·optimizers,·schedulers,·data-loaders·/·augmentations,·and·reference·training·/·validation·scripts·that·aim·to·pull·together·a·wide·variety·of·SOTA·models·with·ability·to·reproduce·ImageNet·training·results.378 Py**T**orch·**Im**age·**M**odels·(`timm`)·is·a·collection·of·image·models,·layers,·utilities,·optimizers,·schedulers,·data-loaders·/·augmentations,·and·reference·training·/·validation·scripts·that·aim·to·pull·together·a·wide·variety·of·SOTA·models·with·ability·to·reproduce·ImageNet·training·results.
  
377 The·work·of·many·others·is·present·here.·I've·tried·to·make·sure·all·source·material·is·acknowledged·via·links·to·github,·arxiv·papers,·etc·in·the·README,·documentation,·and·code·docstrings.·Please·let·me·know·if·I·missed·anything.379 The·work·of·many·others·is·present·here.·I've·tried·to·make·sure·all·source·material·is·acknowledged·via·links·to·github,·arxiv·papers,·etc·in·the·README,·documentation,·and·code·docstrings.·Please·let·me·know·if·I·missed·anything.
